          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9796710606" href="/book/show/18341063-cartas-portuguesas">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/25076181-graciosa-reis?shelf=correspond%C3%AAncia">correspondência</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/25076181-graciosa-reis?shelf=tenho-livro">tenho-livro</a>, 
